Many Ukrainian soldiers and civilians are and will die only for the egotistical interests of the USA, as it is not possible that both Europe, together with Ukraine, are being sacrificed for only these interests of the USA.
   It is wrong that Russia invaded Ukraine, but it was Ukraine's fault for not respecting the Minsk treaties
   It is not possible that the Western countries together with the USA want to cover with a finger the atrocities that Ukraine had committed against Donbas and Luhansk for long time and nobody said nothing and now they're crying over something they brought on themselves.
 In March when it seemed that there were peace talks between Ukraine and Russia, the USA is going to immediately intervene and manipulate Zelensky to continue this war.
   It is already too late and Ukraine has already lost these territories now from Russia and even if Ukraine and the USA do what they do, they will not be able to recover these territories again.
    Russia's temporary withdrawal right now is just a strategy and it makes it look like Ukraine is advancing, but little missing for the next move and against Russia's attack it's all a matter of time. 
   Peace will only come if the USA and NATO stop interfering. The only thing that will be achieved is that Russia may get all of Ukraine.
